name: "Front Bank:3077
description:
This is my design proposal of what the famous Frost Bank Tower in downtown Austin, Texas will potentially look like in the year, 3077. This cool minty image was created in Adobe Illustrator from a hand-drawn sketch circa January 2021. The original drawing of this shape was created in downtown Las Vegas circa 2019. 

"Frost Bank:3077" is part of the newest "Scavenger" series from the geometric abstract artist Gadfly. This series contains 7 unique "Portals" that have been created specifically for NFTs and digital animation and are simply the skeletons for the official release the "Scavenger" series to be artwork on my next album.
